#: ../../../../release/_9.2-stripped.md:237
msgid ""
"The parallel coordinates chart now supports multiple selections on the same "
"axis. This includes addition, subtraction, and toggle actions."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.2-stripped.md:243
msgid ""
"The `vtkGenerateTimeSteps` filter may be used to add timesteps to shallow-"
"copied data within a pipeline."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.2-stripped.md:245
msgid ""
"The `vtkHyperTreeGridGradient` filter may be used to compute a gradient over "
"a scalar field. The edges of the dual is used, so all neighbors are "
"considered, but coarse cells are ignored."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.2-stripped.md:248
msgid ""
"The `vtkExtractParticlesOverTime` filter may extract particles over time "
"that pass through a given volumetric dataset."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.2-stripped.md:250
msgid ""
"`vtkMultiObjectMassProperties` now also computes the centroids of each "
"object. Centroids are calculated using tetrahedron centroids and uniform "
"density."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.2-stripped.md:253
msgid ""
"`vtkJoinTables` may perform a SQL-style `JOIN` operation on two `vtkTable` "
"objects. The columns to keep depend on the mode: `intersection` (keep "
"columns common to both tables), `union` (keeps columns present in either "
"table), and `left` and `right` (keeping the keys present in the respective "
"input table)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.2-stripped.md:257
msgid ""
"`vtkComputeQuantiles` has been split out of `vtkComputeQuartiles` as a new "
"superclass. It supports arbitrary numbers of buckets."
msgstr ""

