#: ../../../../release/_9.2-stripped.md:295
msgid ""
"The new `vtkLinearTransformCellLocator` is a cell locator adaptor which can "
"calculate a transformation matrix from a base dataset to another dataset. "
"This matrix is then used to perform cell locator operations. The "
"`UseAllPoints()` method may be used to use either all dataset points (if the "
"transformation might not be linear) or, at most, 100 sample points sampled "
"uniformly from the dataset's point array."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.2-stripped.md:301
msgid ""
"`vtkCellLocator`, `vtkStaticCellLocator`, `vtkCellTreeLocator`, "
"`vtkModifiedBSPTree`, and `vtkLinearTransformCellLocator` each have numerous "
"improvements:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.2-stripped.md:304
msgid "support for `ShallowCopy()`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.2-stripped.md:305
msgid "caching cell bounds has been multithreaded"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.2-stripped.md:306
msgid "`InsideCellBounds` checks are now cached"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.2-stripped.md:307
msgid ""
"new `IntersectWithLine` methods sorted by a parametric `t`; this also "
"provides `FindCellsAlongLine` for each locator"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.2-stripped.md:309
msgid "the `tolerance` parameter may be used to check cell bound intersections"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.2-stripped.md:310
msgid ""
"The `UseExistingSearchStructure` parameter may be used to not rebuild "
"locators when component data changes, but the geometry stays the same; use "
"`ForceBuildLocator` to rebuild as needed in this case"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.2-stripped.md:313
msgid "`vtkCellTreeLocator` supports 64bit IDs."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.2-stripped.md:314
msgid ""
"`vtkCellTreeLocator::IntersectWithLine()` and `vtkModifiedBSPTree::"
"IntersectWithLine()` are now thread-safe."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.2-stripped.md:316
msgid "`vtkCellLocator` is now fully thread-safe."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.2-stripped.md:317
msgid ""
"The `vtkAlignImageDataSetFilter` has been added which can align image "
"datasets to share a single global origin and offset extents in each "
"component image accordingly. All images must use the same spacing."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.2-stripped.md:320
msgid ""
"The new `vtkLengthDistribution` filter may be used to estimate the range of "
"geometric length scales preset in a `vtkDataSet`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.2-stripped.md:322
msgid ""
"`vtkImageMathematics` can now perform operations on more than two images. "
"Rather than connecting a second image to port 1, all connections are made to "
"port 0 instead. This unifies behavior with other repeatable image filters "
"such as `vtkImageAppend`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.2-stripped.md:326
msgid ""
"VTKm's `vtkmContour` filter may be used as a factory override for "
"`vtkContourFilter`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.2-stripped.md:328
msgid ""
"VTKm filter factory overrides may be toggled using `vtkmFilterOverrides::"
"SetEnabled()`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.2-stripped.md:330
msgid "The `vtkExtractHistogram` filter has been moved from ParaView into VTK."
msgstr ""

