"of either `CellCenter` or `FaceCenter`. The behavior may be selected by "
"setting `vtkCGNSReader::DataLocation` to `vtkCGNSReader::CELL_DATA` (the "
"default and previous behavior) or `vtkCGNSReader::FACE_DATA`."
